WITHDRAWALDESCRIPTION: Change in transfer agent and registrar
Registrant never acted as Transfer Agent for any security. Registrant was unable to begin agency as initially intended.  Date shown under 7 below is effective date of TA1 filing.
The registrant was acquired by Computershare Trust Company of Canada ('CTCC') on June 14, 2005. The registrant will be wound up and all clients have been assigned to CTCC effective November 1, 2008.
Registrant has retained an independent transfer agent to perform this function

The Registrant provided transfer agency services only to two affiliated mutual funds and transferred its obligation to provide these services to Principal Shareholder Services, Inc., an affiliated entity, as part of a business consolidation effort.
